(13, 1, '2015-05-12 22:25:35', '2015-05-12 13:25:35', '			现在我们运营以下公众账号\r\n		<h3 class="widget-title">日本窗</h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_64" align="alignnone" width="140"]<img class="wp-image-64 size-full" title="日本窗" src="http://localhost/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/20150318041545942.jpg" alt="1c386920 copy" width="140" height="140"> 粉丝数：38万[/caption]\r\n\r\n\r\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-52" style="position: absolute; top: 55px; left: 55px;" src="http://localhost/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/win_in_japan.jpg" alt="win_in_japan" width="40" height="40">\r\n\r\n透过日本窗,看日本一切,来自日本,原汁原味:最全日本产品,最新日本资讯,最深日本解读.关注即可查询庞大资料库(药妆 日语 文化 旅游 美食 动漫 电影 音乐),数十万人最爱的共同选择.<h3 class="widget-title">日本微商会</h3>\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_71" align="alignnone" width="140"]<img class="wp-image-71 size-medium" src="http://localhost/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/japan-weshop-300x300.jpg" alt="japan-weshop" width="140" height="140"> 粉丝数：8万[/caption]\r\n\r\n日本微商唯一发布平台。最新最快最全日本产品信息<h3 class="widget-title">看日本</h3>\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_64" align="alignnone" width="140"]<img class="wp-image-64 size-full" src="http://localhost/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/japan_business-1.jpg" alt="1c386920 copy" width="140" height="140"> 粉丝数：5万[/caption]\r\n\r\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-52" style="position: absolute; top: 55px; left: 55px;" src="http://localhost/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/japan_business-2.jpg" alt="win_in_japan" width="45" height="45">\r\n\r\n\r\n从日本提供原汁原味咨询，每天带你看真实的日本。<h3 class="widget-title">酵素美人计</h3>\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_79" align="alignnone" width="140"]<img class="wp-image-79 size-medium" src="http://localhost/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/jiaosumeirenji-300x300.jpg" alt="jiaosumeirenji" width="140" height="140"> 粉丝数：4万[/caption]\r\n\r\n\r\n酵素，健康与美丽的源泉。每天普及酵素知识，减肥养生终身美人。<h3 class="widget-title">日本微生活</h3>\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_81" align="alignnone" width="140"]<img class="wp-image-81 size-full" src="http://localhost/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/jpvlife-1.jpg" alt="jpvlife-1" width="140" height="140"> 粉丝数：5万[/caption]\r\n\r\n\r\n源自日本精华资讯，每周八篇精彩文章：全方位网罗日本生活方方面面，融入日本生活不二选择。&nbsp;', '自媒体', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', '%e3%82%a4%e3%83%b3%e3%82%bf%e3%83%8d%e3%83%83%e3%83%88%e3%83%9e%e3%83%bc%e3%82%b1%e3%83%86%e3%82%a3%e3%83%b3%e3%82%b0', '', '', '2015-05-17 10:18:12', '2015-05-17 01:18:12', '', 11, 'http://nebula8090.sakura.ne.jp/c/?page_id=13', 2, 'page', '', 0),
